title: Microsoft Professional Plus 2019 Preview 1806
description:
Microsoft Professional Plus 2019 Preview 1806 (Build 16.0.10217.20000)

Suported Language: DE-DE, EN-US, ES-ES, FR-FR, PT-BR (detection based on your system language)

Need to do:

    1. Uninstall Microsoft Office 2016
    2. Windows 10 Installed (Windows 8.1/8/7/Vista are not supported)
	
How to Install:
	3. Execute Office.exe and extract to desktop or somewhere else (It's a 7zip compressed file - no BS... promise)
	4. If not already there, copy "Office" folder to your Desktop (When done it will look like C:Users"Your_Username"DesktopOffice)
	5. a. In the "Office" folder on your desktop, please execute "Office2019Preview.bat" 
	   or 
	   a. Open CMD (Open Command Prompt)
       b. Type: cd desktop then Press "Enter"
       c. Type: setup.exe /configure configuration.xml then Press "Enter"
	   
How to Update: File>Account>Office Updates
	   
Read more: https://techhelpday.com/microsoft-office-2019/
